de.tavendo.autobahn

类 PrefixMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tavendo.autobahn.PrefixMap

  • public class PrefixMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Mapping between CURIEs and URIs. Provides a two-way mapping between CURIEs (Compact URI Expressions) and full URIs. \see http://www.w3.org/TR/curie/ \todo Prefixes MUST be NCNames (http://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xml-names-19990114/#NT-NCName) \todo Work in the details of http://www.w3.org/TR/curie/ (default prefixes, ..)

    • 方法详细资料

      • set

        public void set(java.lang.String prefix,
                java.lang.String uri)
        Set mapping of prefix to URI.
        参数:
        prefix - Prefix to be mapped.
        uri - URI the prefix is to be mapped to.

      • get

        public java.lang.String get(java.lang.String prefix)
        Returns the URI for the prefix or None if prefix has no mapped URI.
        参数:
        prefix - Prefix to look up.
        返回:
        Mapped URI for prefix or None.

      • remove

        public java.lang.String remove(java.lang.String prefix)
        Remove mapping of prefix to URI.
        参数:
        prefix - Prefix for which mapping should be removed.
        返回:
        The URI the prefix was mapped to (when removed), or null when prefix is unmapped (so there wasn't anything to remove).

      • clear

        public void clear()
        Remove all prefix mappings.

      • resolve

        public java.lang.String resolve(java.lang.String curie)
        Resolve given CURIE to full URI.
        参数:
        curie - CURIE (i.e. "rdf:label").
        返回:
        Full URI for CURIE or None.

      • resolveOrPass

        public java.lang.String resolveOrPass(java.lang.String curieOrUri)
        Resolve given CURIE/URI and return string verbatim if cannot be resolved.
        参数:
        curieOrUri - CURIE or URI.
        返回:
        Full URI for CURIE or original string.

      • shrink

        public java.lang.String shrink(java.lang.String uri)
        Shrink given URI to CURIE. If no appropriate prefix mapping is available, return original URI.
        参数:
        uri - URI to shrink.
        返回:
        CURIE or original URI.
